    "body": "Sorry, I asked three questions and these were not well-separated.\n1. Is calling another matplotlib backend from another backend (=ipython inline backend) possible?  (Putting aside IPython and zmq, it is a pure Python question.)\n2. It means calling backend function from kernel Python instance, not from frontend Python instance, right?  Meaning that you cannot use it via ssh unless you have X port forwarded and having some functions to treat DISPLAY environment.  Am I correct?\n3. Do you think these functions fit with IPython?\n"
